# Functional Correlates
- [Dimensionality Reduction](Dimensionality%20Reduction.qmd) technique used to quantify the [Correlation](Correlation.qmd) and dependence between two variables when the data is functional
- Relations between the surface and phenomena that influence or are influenced by the topography.
